<div class="patternContent"><div class="foswikiTopic"> <h1 id="SiteTopicActions">  <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/SiteTopicActions">SiteTopicActions</a> </h1>
Default <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="/bin/view/System/SiteTopicActions">SiteTopicActions</a> component. Please do <strong><em>not</em></strong> modify. Use <a class="foswikiNewLink" href="/bin/edit/Main/SiteTopicActions?topicparent=System.SiteTopicActions" rel="nofollow" title="Create this topic">SiteTopicActions</a> instead.
<p></p>

<h2 id="Implementation">  Implementation </h2>
<pre class="tml">
